room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: We did the Cabin Fever room. We almost made it! It was very fun. The staff was great and very helpful. They didn't just let us flounder around with no direction. We had a group of 3. It really helped retrying #'s with the locks. We had a couple that one person tried, and didn't get. Then, another person tried it and it worked! It was a fun thing to do, and got us out of the house for a bit!

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: Cabin Fever was a hard one for us! We had a blast!

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: This was so fun! I wasn't at all sure what to expect, but we will definitely be back. We did "Cabin Fever," and it for sure lived up to our expectations. The flow of the puzzle was super creative, and there were a lot of twists and turns that kept it exciting.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: Awesome room had a lot of fun. It was challenging but still achievable.
